==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Patriots Day
<hw>Pa"tri*ots' Day</hw>. <def>A legal holiday in the States of
Massachusetts and Maine, April 19, the anniversary of the battle of
Lexington in 1775. It was first observed in 1894.</def> <mark>[U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

